body:
Note that I had actually filed https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-1720 to switch all of Spark (not just spark on yarn) to use LD_LIBRARY_PATH to try to keep it consistent across Spark if possible.

@pwendell @mateiz do you have any objections to switching to use LD_LIBRARY_PATH?   If any questions about it then we should remove that change from this PR and just fix yarn-client mode to work with spark.executor.extraLibraryPath and handle the change under SPARK-1720.

@pwendell  @mateiz are you aware of anyone using hadoop 2.x before 2.0.2-alpha?  I haven't seen any queries about it but there are 2.0.1-alpha and 2.0.0-alpha.
